      "text": "Woo yeah",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 34.8,
      "time_str": "00:34.800",
      "text": "气温 爬升到无法再忍受",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 41.29,
      "time_str": "00:41.290",
      "text": "索性闭上了双眼",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 44.19,
