      "text": "让想象任意改变",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 49.24,
      "time_str": "00:49.240",
      "text": "场景 两个人一起散着步",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 53.72,
      "time_str": "00:53.720",
      "text": "我的脸也轻轻贴着你胸口",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
